   {[}14-14-00250] Funding Source: Russian Science Foundation},
Funding-Text = {The author is very grateful to A. N. Kuznetsov and S. P. Kuznetsova for
   help in organization of fieldwork in Vietnam. The author is grateful to
   the staff of the Laboratory of Electron Microscopy of the Biological
